 were Giant Shimano and Omega Quick Step guys with us and I banked on them to chase for a mass sprint and we nearly got it. In my mind, riders like [Vincenzo] Nibali or Betancur still remain the favourites, they have more GC [general classification] experience than I do.\"</p><p>He added: \"Tomorrow will be a hard day with a 220-something stage and a steep hill finale. I hope to be there or thereabouts.\"</p>","headline":"Geraint Thomas retains Paris-Nice lead but Carlos Betancur wins stage","trailText":"Team Sky's Geraint Thomas kept the yellow jersey after finishing 16th on the 153-kilometre section of the Paris-Nice race, which was won by Carlos Betancur","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Sport/Pix/columnists/2014/3/13/1394734957943/Geraint-Thomas-rides-in-t-006.jpg","wordcount":"173","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2014-03-16T18:34:08Z"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2014/mar/13/geraint-thomas-paris-nice-carlos-betancur-team-sky","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/sport/2014/mar/13/geraint-thomas-paris-nice-carlos-betancur-team-sky","tags":[{"id":"sport/team-sky","webTitle":"Team Sky","type":"keyword","sectionId":"sport","sectionName":"Sport","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/sport/team-sky","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/sport/team-sky","references":[]},{"id":"sport/cycling","webTitle":"Cycling","type":"keyword","sectionId":"sport","sectionName":"Sport","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/sport/cycling","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/sport/cycling","references":[]},{"id":"sport/sport","webTitle":"Sport","type":"keyword","sectionId":"sport","sectionName":"Sport","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/sport/sport","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/sport/sport","references":[]},{"id":"tone/news","webTitle":"News","type":"tone","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/tone/news","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/tone/news","references":[]},{"id":"type/artic