y for me.\"</p><p>A competent climber, Thomas will be the favourite to keep the yellow jersey in Thursday's fifth stage, which takes the peloton over 95 miles from Crêches-sur-Saône to Rive-de-Gier and features four modest hills.</p>","headline":"Geraint Thomas takes lead in Paris-Nice race after fourth-stage sprint","trailText":"Geraint Thomas finished second behind Tom-Jelte Slagter to head the Paris-Nice race after being given the responsibility of leading Team Sky","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Sport/Pix/columnists/2014/3/12/1394641493700/Team-Skys-Geraint-Thomas--006.jpg","wordcount":"217","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2014-03-15T16:30:52Z"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2014/mar/12/geraint-thomas-paris-nice-race-fourth-stage-team-sky","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/sport/2014/mar/12/geraint-thomas-paris-nice-race-fourth-stage-team-sky","tags":[{"id":"sport/team-sky","webTitle":"Team Sky","type":"keyword","sectionId":"sport","sectionName":"Sport","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/sport/team-sky","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/sport/team-sky","references":[]},{"id":"sport/cycling","webTitle":"Cycling","type":"keyword","sectionId":"sport","sectionName":"Sport","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/sport/cycling","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/sport/cycling","references":[]},{"id":"sport/sport","webTitle":"Sport","type":"keyword","sectionId":"sport","sectionName":"Sport","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/sport/sport","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/sport/sport","references":[]},{"id":"tone/news","webTitle":"News","type":"tone","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/tone/news","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/tone/news","references":[]},{"id":"type/article","webTitle":"Article","type":"type","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/articles","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/type/article","references":[]}],"references":[],"element